.TH "pci_set_vga_state" 9 "pci_set_vga_state" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pci_set_vga_state \- set VGA decode state on device and parents if requested
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" pci_set_vga_state
.BI "(struct pci_dev *dev "  ","
.BI "bool decode "  ","
.BI "unsigned int command_bits "  ","
.BI "u32 flags "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
the PCI device
.IP "decode" 12
true = enable decoding, false = disable decoding
.IP "command_bits" 12
PCI_COMMAND_IO and/or PCI_COMMAND_MEMORY
.IP "flags" 12
traverse ancestors and change bridges
CHANGE_BRIDGE_ONLY / CHANGE_BRIDGE
